          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "Graphs have costs\n\nA graph is just points connected by edges. Each edge has a weight, like time, distance, or money.\n\n- Nodes are places\n- Edges are connections\n- Weights are costs\n- Goal is cheapest route",
