        "layoutPreset": "split_text_left_canvas_right",
        "elements": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "A tiny test graph\n\nStart at A. The direct route to B costs 5, but going through C can be cheaper. Dijkstra will prove it step by step.\n\n- A → B costs 5\n- A → C costs 1\n- C → D costs 1\n- Best A → D is 2",
            "iconName": "BarChart3",
            "width": null,
            "height": null,
            "x": 116,
            "y": 148,
            "animation": "fade"
          },
          {
            "type": "image",
